        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 8. — Paranursallia spinosa gen. and sp. nov.Holotype MNHN.F.PSA214.The ventral keel scutes, the ventral and cloacal scales and the beginning of the anal fin. Abbreviations:CLT, cleithrum;LEP, pelvic and anal fins rays;PCB, postcoelomic bone;RAD, anal pterygiophores;SC, ventral scales of the abdominal region; SC c.1-3, cloacal scales 1 to 3; SCU 1-8, precloacal ventral keel scutes 1 to 8; SCU 9-10, postcloacal ventral keel scutes. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
